PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of each of the following persons as a director of the Board of Directors of the Export Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years: DOROTHY E. BYRNE, Vancouver, B.C., in the place of Jonathan Deitcher; M. JANE MARTIN, Mississauga, Ontario, in the place of Bruce Sully; and JAMES A. PATTILLO, Calgary, Alberta, in the place of Timothy A. Chisholm
